BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:ZPDJcN2CIdP9kseGc0XJY
SUMMARY:Grand Opening - AI & Robotics Academy
DTSTAMP:20260307T234436Z
DTSTART:20260321T120000Z
DESCRIPTION:Come celebrate the grand opening of AI & Robotics Academy in Ma
	gnolia. \\nWe offer comprehensive after-school programs (with local school
	 pickup)\\\, morning “Little Innovators” classes\\\, weekend competition p
	rep\\\, and immersive camps designed to build “forever skills” like logic 
	and collaborative problem-solving. \\nWe will have special opening day wor
	kshops\\\, exclusive discounts and offers\\\, and light snacks.\n\nhttps:/
	/discovermagnolia.org/event/grand-opening-ai-robotics-academy/\n\nFrom Dis
	cover Magnolia
